attributes.action: Bring net immigration into the UK to below 30,000 per year
attributes.additional_details: David Kurten AM is a politician who I think is a good politician to consult on this matter- his arguments are very good.
attributes.background:
Immigration into this country is simply too high. 
Mass immigration has negative economic effects, but more importantly, negative social and cultural effects, made worse by the terrible policy of multiculturalism.
Therefore we ask the government to cap net immigration at 30,000 per year.
